          "reviewBody": "Myself jaison\nCame for interschool skating competition for participation for my son and had a very bad experience. We reported by 7.25 am and we waited till 3.30 pm for the event. But not still called. There is no scheduledor the event . At least school or who ever authorised can make a schedule for inline and code by age wise and saying this please be on time mentioned for code under 13 please come by whatever time but what happened is all students were requested to come by 7.25am. When i asked the skating miss she told everwhere this is the style i cant donanything. Please dont organise if ate not able to do\nVery bad\nNo organisation for the event\nAssisi School teachers are also very rude who were sitting in the certificate distribution. When i asked y this is happening. The lady with specs i doesn’t know her name she was least bothered and i said i will be putting a google review she said u can what ever you feel like. So from that i understood that if a google review comes for assisi vidyanikenthan chembukku there is nothing for school authorities. Parents i requesy who ever faced this issue please write a google review let them understand. I doesn’t know as per the lady whether they bother",
